| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-6037 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6ad2ecce-b1e1-5161-986c-25be7ad728b8"
